  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients who have sleep disorders may be involved in accidents more frequently than those
      without. In addition patients who have sleep disorders may have more serious accidents and
      have increased length of stay.We aim to recruit drivers admitted as a result of a motor
      vehicle accidents and to ascertain the prevalence of sleep disorders in this group.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
